---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Portfolio">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Shrey Chauhan</h1>
      
      <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        Hi, I’m Shrey — an engineer who loves building systems, solving problems, and playing 1-minute chess between tasks. I’m also passionate about sports.
      </p>
      </br>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        I graduated from NIT Trichy in 2014 with a degree in Computer Science. During college, I led the dance team as its president, and many of my leadership qualities trace back to that experience. Navigating the team through victories, failures, and crises taught me resilience, responsibility, and how to inspire people.
      </p>
      </br>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        I’m a Senior Engineering Manager at Quantum, where I lead the Unified Surveillance Platform (USP) engineering team. USP is Quantum’s optimized hyperconverged infrastructure solution for large-scale video surveillance.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        Before this, I was one of the founding engineers at EnCloudEn, where I led engineering for our virtual desktop, private cloud, and HCI platforms. I joined as the second engineer, became Director of Engineering, and helped grow a 15-member team that built the technology foundation that ultimately led to EnCloudEn’s acquisition by Quantum.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- About AI Section -->
    <section id="about" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 border-b-2 border-gray-300 pb-2">So… what exactly is AI?</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          AI is the biggest buzzword in tech today, and like many engineers, I’ve been diving deep into it. Since my day-to-day work doesn’t revolve around AI, I began taking on side projects to learn, experiment, and document my progress. I genuinely believe that AI is something every software engineer should explore, because it marks a major paradigm shift in how we build software—We’ve moved from machine code to assembly to high-level languages… and now to AI-assisted development.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Achievements</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Achievement 1: [Description of your achievement]</li>
          <li>Achievement 2: [Description of your achievement]</li>
          <li>Achievement 3: [Description of your achievement]</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Work/Projects Section -->
    <section id="work" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 border-b-2 border-gray-300 pb-2">AI Work & Projects</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <article class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline">
              Project Title 1
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
            [Brief description of your AI project. What problem did it solve? What technologies did you use?]
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Technologies: Python, TensorFlow, PyTorch</p>
        </article>

        <article class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline">
              Project Title 2
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
            [Brief description of another AI project. Include key highlights and outcomes.]
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Technologies: Python, Scikit-learn, Pandas</p>
        </article>

        <article class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline">
              Project Title 3
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
            [Description of your third project. Focus on the AI/ML aspects and your contributions.]
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Technologies: Python, FastAPI, Docker</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Blog Section -->
    <section id="blog" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 border-b-2 border-gray-300 pb-2">Blog Posts</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">1.</span>
          <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline text-lg">
            Understanding Neural Networks: A Beginner's Guide
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">2.</span>
          <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline text-lg">
            Building My First ML Model: Lessons Learned
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">3.</span>
          <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline text-lg">
            The Future of AI in Healthcare
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">4.</span>
          <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline text-lg">
            Deep Learning vs Traditional ML: When to Use What
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">5.</span>
          <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline text-lg">
            My Journey into Computer Vision
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-300">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-900">Resume</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-900">GitHub</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-900">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-900">Email</a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
        © 2024 Your Name. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

